stimulus:
If this is your first time doing this experiment, your browser will ask you for permission to use the webcam and microphone.

Please click on "Accept"/"Allow", as both of them are needed for the study to work.

Dont worry: Doing so will only grant permission to this study, other sites won't be able to access your webcam and microphone.

Please accept the browsers popup and press the "Continue" button afterwards.

Press the "Submit" button below to transmit your data to us.

The upload will take 1-2 minutes, after which you will be redirected to the next slide automatically. Please leave this tab open until you get new instructions.

The Webcam icon in your browser will still display, however, no new recordings will be created..
